name: FinCypher
description: The FinCypher token has several roles in the system: first, it is applied as a base currency in the Fincypher ecosystem for the trade of Fincypher Crypto CDOs, next the token is used as a mean of payment of the relayer fees, and lastly token drives the governance process in Fincypher ecosystem allowing stakeholders to securely execute Fincypher protocol upgrades.
